Pass the Cisco CCNA 200-301 Exam on you first attempt. Questions with solutions and references.

This exam tests your knowledge and skills related to:

20% 1.0 Network Fundamentals 20% 2.0 Network Access 25% 3.0 IP Connectivity 10% 4.0 IP Services 15% 5.0 Security Fundamentals 10% 6.0 Automation and Programmability Exam Description

The Cisco Certified Network Associate v1.0 (CCNA 200-301) exam is a 120-minute exam associated with the CCNA certification. This exam tests a candidate’s knowledge and skills related to network fundamentals, network access, IP connectivity, IP services, security fundamentals, and automation and programmability. The course, Implementing and Administering Cisco Solutions (CCNA), helps candidates prepare for this exam. What our students say:

“Superb. I recently got my certification with other exams, and just passed my Cisco CCNA 200-301 exam. Very happy with Ultimate exams. Thank you” Helena Johnson

“Fantastic real exam questions and all are up to date. I will definitely recommend this to my colleagues and friends” Karthik

Note: Please note that you are responsible for registering and paying for the actual exam.
